description:
This is a 46 minute workout called '45 MIN MILITARY MONDAY Killer HIIT Workout - Full Body, No Equipment, No Repeat' from the channel growingannanas.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Tactical Athlete vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate and Advanced.
The effort required is Challenging.
